{"type": "article", "id": 24009, "title": "儿童画一样的包装", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-17T07:00:23Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 61, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607104138ZgSloCQw3I0cRqmh.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这款酒产自格鲁吉亚，它的名字 RANINA 源于当地的歌曲。包装上用近乎儿童画的笔调画出了一幅载歌载舞的风俗画，有拟人化的太阳和月亮，充满了弯曲的纹路和异域风情。背后的条纹码上也有小的图案，非常有趣。这一系列 5 种酒的图案是一样的，只在服饰和名字上面用了不同颜色的晕染，显示出不同的品种。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016060710413624OfFWTzSbChPMDs.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104137wxXE1eC9Vu70J2YA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104137KnfrlszcNCjOgkmF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70740741\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}